# Guidelines for Transcriboquest 2025

Trainers : Federica Nicolardi, Marianne Reboul

Introduction : This document outlines a proposed set of transcription guidelines for the Handwritten Text Recognition (HTR) of Ancient Greek documents, intended to support the development of generalizable and robust HTR models. This document is based on the existing work in progress from TranscriboQuest2024 (Mathilde Verstraete, Maxime GuÃ©nette, Marianne Reboul) and DH2025 (Mathilde Verstraete, Maxime GuÃ©nette, Mathenia Vlachou, Marianne Reboul).
